[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    548[0m:[38;5;10m[49m                             (a cookie, an app token, a phone number);
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    549[0m:[38;5;10m[49m                             used to thread turns into a session.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    550[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         user_message:       The patient's typed message.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    551[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         language:           Detected or declared language; defaults
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    552[0m:[38;5;10m[49m                             to en-US for the demo.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    553[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    554[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Returns:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    555[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         A dict with the response to send to the user. The
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    556[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         response may be a greeting + answer, a refusal-and-handoff,
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    557[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         a crisis response, or a clarifying question.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    558[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
