[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1346[0m:[38;5;10m[49m def _source_title_from_result(result: dict) -> str:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1347[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1348[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Extract a human-readable source title from a result. The
