[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2076[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```python
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2077[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # --- Mocks for the demo. In production these are real AWS calls. ---
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2078[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2079[0m:[38;5;10m[49m class MockTable:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2080[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
